{"tid":1570838,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]警方將於中環及金鐘展開驅散行動 2019-09-15 HKT 16:48","createTime":"2019-09-15T09:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T09:02:30.000Z","uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c344a1e25c939d4f992b10b585d4975ac857a525","tid":1570838,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T09:02:30.000Z","msg":"警方表示，下午四時半開始，激進示威者於中環及金鐘多處縱火，有激進示威者破壞並堵塞金鐘站的出入口，夏慤道近政府總部的來回行車線亦被堵塞。警方將會在短時間內驅散示威者。<br />\n<br />\n警方警告示威者立刻停止所有違法行為，並離開現場，並呼籲市民避免前往金鐘、中環一帶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480673-20190915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480673-20190915.htm&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=7e6fcefe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480673-20190915.htm&h=8292f646\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480673-20190915.htm</a>"}]}